of their many natures for you.

86
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:32,731
No, don't move.

87
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:35,455
Watch how I track them down.

88
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,973
Filthy little things.

89
00:07:38,380 --> 00:07:40,848
Sadistic little devils.

90
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:42,854
Don't be afraid.

91
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:44,732
Leave her alone, Doc.

92
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:47,017
I'm just removing a little worm.

93
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:49,857
Just leave her alone.

94
00:07:50,060 --> 00:07:51,698
Come with me.
I have to tell you something.

95
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:53,492
Just a second, she wants me...

96
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:56,698
This is urgent. Come with me.

97
00:07:57,020 --> 00:07:58,897
Afraid I might hurt her?

98
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,215
You know I...

99
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:23,251
- Waiter.
- Yes, ma'am.

100
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:25,498
Give me a drink.

101
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:32,889
What d'they all have against me?

102
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:38,889
Waiter.

103
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:41,091
Yes, ma'am. The same?

104
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:42,415
No. Have any cigarettes?

105
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:44,099
I'll see.

106
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:49,336
Mario will drive him home.

107
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:51,849
May I?

108
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:57,329
Did he scare you?

109
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:01,010
It's nothing.
He's a charming fellow.

110
00:09:03,260 --> 00:09:04,170
Cheers!

111
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:05,935
Here's to you.

112
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:12,058
You realize he's a junkie.
He left you to have a shot.

113
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:14,819
Known him long?

114
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:15,975
No.

115
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:20,330
His name's Bernard.
He was a doctor in Versailles.

116
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:23,579
I'm thirsty.

117
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:28,296
You're a real hit with Alan.

118
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:31,537
He keeps ogling you.
He's on his 8th scotch.

119
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:34,979
If it makes him happy.

120
00:09:37,060 --> 00:09:38,573
Mario's back.

121
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:40,939
It's pouring out.

122
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,609
